    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Crushed rock, slate, slag, porcelain, or tile, crushed into particles and graded, used as surfacing on asphalt roofing and shingles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
